<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>و <span class="c4">[النصيَّة]</span>: خيار القوم <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">والنصية:</span> ما اختير من الشيء.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
